Package group19.GameLoop

Class GameLoop

java.lang.Object
java.awt.Component
java.awt.Container
javax.swing.JComponent
javax.swing.JPanel
group19.GameLoop.GameLoop
All Implemented Interfaces:
ActionListener, ImageObserver, MenuContainer, Serializable, Runnable, EventListener, Accessible
public class GameLoop extends JPanel implements Runnable, ActionListener
This class represents the game screen UI and the game loop which loops through the game logic at each tick to display and interpret all things that are needed to run the game.
